  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## ISSUE 1\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nFor Android: if permission to Camera was denied and if you tap to camera icon in 1-1/group chat, pop-up with text \"_To grant the required camera permission, please go to your system settings and make sure that Status > **Photos is selected**_\" will be shown.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nText of error: To grant the required camera permission, please go to your system settings and make sure that Status > **Camera is selected**.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nText of error: To grant the required camera... > **Photos is selected.** \r\n\r\n![ezgif com-resize (16)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/89910048-09b96380-dbf0-11ea-9d34-bda33a030e84.gif)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Install Status and log in\r\n- Open 1-1 or group chat\r\n- Tap Image gallery icon\r\n- Tap Camera icon\r\n- Deny permission\r\n- Tap Camera icon one more time\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: Nightly 11/08\r\n- Operating System: Android 10\r\n\r\n## ISSUE 2\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nFor iOS: if permission to Camera was denied and if you tap to camera icon in 1-1/group chat, pop-up with information (error) about permissions will not appear. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nError \"To grant the required camera permission, please go to your system settings and make sure that Status > Camera is selected\" is expected, as for permission to Image gallery.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nNothing happens after tapping Camera icon, no error/information message.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Install Status and log in\r\n- Open 1-1 or group chat\r\n- Tap Image gallery icon to open Image panel\r\n- Tap Camera icon\r\n- Deny permission\r\n- Tap Camera icon one more time\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: Nightly 11/08\r\n- Operating System: iOS 13",
